  home (closest to the school) and the educational establishment
  attended.   - Application/payment: Reimbursement must be requested
  using the provided form and is paid monthly. The payment is
  calculated using the formula: (km * 2 * EUR 0.40 * 180 school days)
  / 12 (the 180 school days factor is used in the formula).   -
  Changes and timing: If the child’s home or the school changes, the
